detail: MathDQN improves upon ExpressionTree by using deep reinforcement learning to iteratively pick the best operator for two selected quantities.
evidence: MathDQN models the tree construction as a Markov Decision Process and leverages the strengths of deep Q-network (DQN) to enhance the accuracy and robustness.
